        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I calculated and combined the <a href="https://medium.com/@oleg.kazanskyi/trading-analytics-with-financial-kpis-cb35fe5c020d" target="_self">15 most important financial KPIs</a> from the public companiesâ€™ published reports.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I scrapped the information about <a href="https://medium.com/@oleg.kazanskyi/trading-analytics-with-financial-kpis-33df3b1cff24" target="_self">the important market conditions and future market expectations</a>.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">I created a test ML model based on 3 years of data<strong> </strong><a href="https://medium.com/@oleg.kazanskyi/75-accuracy-stocks-prediction-based-on-financial-kpis-92ba83177346" target="_self">for DOW30 companies with a 75% prediction score.</a></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
