            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Stock % change in 15 days.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Stock % change in 30 days.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Stock % change in 60 days.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Stock % change in 90 days.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Stock % change in 120 days.</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Stock % change in 150 days.</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
